rComments: I loved learning from Prof. Aitchison. She worked really hard to build an interesting class, and we learned from a variety of sources. She helped guide our discussions but let us learn and talk and never shot anything down. A lot of professors I find kind of shoot you down and make you feel dumb when asking your opinion, but she just uplifted.

Professor Aitchison is amazing, and probably one of the best professors I've had at uO. The content was so interesting, her lectures are easy to follow, and she really encourages questioning and discussion, particularly questioning her and the validity of every source we use. She really cares about her students and understands uni struggles. 12/10
